Package: functracer
Title: Trace Function Dependencies in R Code
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kelly", "Sovacool", , "kelly.sovacool@nih.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3283-829X")),
    person("CCR Collaborative Bioinformatics Resource", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Build direct and transitive function dependency graphs from an
    R entry script and a target package source tree. Exports machine-readable
    and human-readable artifacts (CSV, JSON, SVG) for analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/CCBR/functracer
